  "ai_usage": "Use for retro flat-design headings, logos, and icons. The shadow is a comma-separated list of text-shadows at 1px,2px,3px… offsets in a darker hue. Generate the long list with a loop (Sass @for, PostCSS, or build-time JS) rather than hand-typing. Keep to large display text; avoid on paragraphs for performance.",
